{"tid":491643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一世有陰影！陳敏之坐港鐵曾遭揭裙底","createTime":"2017-12-06T17:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T17:44:28.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9783ddad1aca6259ff74c64aa59476b2eca850a3","tid":491643,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"[url]http://202.171.252.18:9999/<a href=\"http://video.cdn.on.cc/Video/201712/OEN171204-9940-1609-M_ipad.mp4?t=1512421812[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.cdn.on.cc%2FVideo%2F201712%2FOEN171204-9940-1609-M_ipad.mp4%3Ft%3D1512421812%5B%2Furl%5D&d=4bvcAMgvGezbI97IR41X%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8a311fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">video.cdn.on.cc/Video/201712/OEN171204-9940-1609-M_ipad.mp4?t=1512421812[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人陳敏之、江美儀和韋家雄在尖沙咀出席無綫互動短劇《再親我好媽》記者會。提到最近爆出多單性侵事件，其中麥明詩更在網上指自己曾遭性侵，陳敏之受訪時坦言會向囝囝雷冬至灌輸正確價值觀：「網上會睇到好多預計唔到嘅嘢，要同佢打定個底，教佢知咩係應該唔應該。」<br />\n<br />\n問有否類似經驗，陳敏之表示十多歲做兼職模特兒時搭地鐵被揭起裙底：「一定係有心，我即刻嗌，好委屈，好想喊，面都紅晒，啲人即刻退後一步，但冇人敢認。（報警？）嗰時太細唔識處理，淨係覺得好驚、好變態，同埋知報警都冇用。」她指此事令她留有陰影：「一世都記得！依家搭地鐵都會黐牆企，同擺個狠樣出嚟。」所以她絕對贊成設立女性車廂，以及鼓勵女生學防狼術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171204/bkn-20171204160930152-1204_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171204%2Fbkn-20171204160930152-1204_00862_001.html&d=4bvcAMgvGezbI97IR41X%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e733a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171204/bkn-20171204160930152-1204_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"353c848db0474180e667fcdae2fa3e7a16715297","tid":491643,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a5a8a1ba5318153f7c6aeb82b6f7430c598f14","tid":491643,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"#警察無用<br />\n#法治已死"},{"pid":"de60c5ea21ba086ac4ae4da12ee20a383907e51b","tid":491643,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"2512606f220c43584b9eec7efb6cb6b6a067dc18","tid":491643,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"俾我都想揭啦, me too <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}